            "title": "Pan Pacific Hotels Group Elevates the Business Events Experience with \"Every Meeting Matters\" Campaign",
            "id": "595c14a9-c59a-4ec9-996d-c437d6287a98",
            "description": "The Pan Pacific Hotels Group (PPHG) is focusing on repositioning its meetings and events sector as part of its overall strategy to enhance its group-wide meetings and events spaces, with a goal of becoming a reliable partner for impactful and high-quality meetings and events. This initiative is taking place on a global scale and is being spearheaded by the company headquarters in Singapore. As of March 24, 2026, the PPHG is emphasizing its commitment to the MICE (Meetings, Incentives, Conferences, and Exhibitions) market with a significant push towards this segment. The company aims to solidify its presence and reputation in this sector through its ongoing efforts and enhancements in meeting and event services.",
